ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLife大如 ing fwd 富通呢d都幾次啦<br />\n<br />\nGI公司更加多到你唔識 上保監都有得睇"},{"pid":"2a0ffa11eefd89b70660738b35d2d9644caeba3b","tid":374173,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實保險咩都唔賠仲有咩意義 買黎做乜</blockquote><br />\n但今次都幾乎咩都賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家就算車保都好多都包打風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賠咪正常 有咩好慶祝 人地收咁多保費 大攪錢 幾時會仆街過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實年中執好多保險公司 特別係財險<br />\n<br />\n如果真係咁好賺唔會成日轉手 而且財險好多保監統計都係賺同蝕之間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬼咩，一個二個Insured買幾百蚊幾千蚊保險就乜都claim, bump到個claims amount上六位甚至七位數。要賣幾多張單先cum到條數，有RI 都咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nproperty都話有限錢，claim EC, liability先難計要預賠幾多，香港好多乞兒識同保險公司玩claims, pro過班claims staff<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班老細都勁仆街 EC買少勁多人頭<br />\n<br />\n同埋車保 長年都係蝕<br />\n<br />\n2011年開始少人交通意外死先賺返錢<br />\n好多後生仔無車唔會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efdad6587ee36f981c40b0f7a151613ff08a8de","tid":374173,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實保險咩都唔賠仲有咩意義 買黎做乜</blockquote><br />\n但今次都幾乎咩都賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家就算車保都好多都包打風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賠咪正常 有咩好慶祝 人地收咁多保費 大攪錢 幾時會仆街過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實年中執好多保險公司 特別係財險<br />\n<br />\n如果真係咁好賺唔會成日轉手 而且財險好多保監統計都係賺同蝕之間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬼咩，一個二個Insured買幾百蚊幾千蚊保險就乜都claim, bump到個claims amount上六位甚至七位數。要賣幾多張單先cum到條數，有RI 都咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nproperty都話有限錢，claim EC, liability先難計要預賠幾多，香港好多乞兒識同保險公司玩claims, pro過班claims staff<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n執又無咁誇張，但係我聽講好多細既財險公司轉手囉，因為佢地要賠好多錢。其實如果唔係有咩大鍋野，一次過賠錢，其實真係賺到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架 無人接手咪執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係保監睇每年財險d名都有加有減 就知其實都有d無人接收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f3efef46753856456d8d58867c1abe04bd2376","tid":374173,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"賠,下年個保費會加,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估保險咁易比你賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c95af0e711bd9eb604951fe8524df467d9105b1","tid":374173,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的士之前話8號都會賠 新聞講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哈哈"},{"pid":"f9f8fe930934be609f3725fb84307e8fc24d8168","tid":374173,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>的士之前話8號都會賠 新聞講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哈哈</blockquote><br />\n乜唔係話係非危險情況下先賠咩<br />\n即係你明知掛緊8號風仲出去<br />\n而8號風又係危險的情況<br />\n所有保險公司唔會賠<br />\n我都係聽新聞講<br />\n<br />\n咁如果8號風載客情況下有意外<br />\n乘客係咪都係向車主/司機追討<br />\n保險公司都係唔會賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700a871a3032a308b570b78433f41ef744012686","tid":374173,"uid":35815,