n咁如果8號風載客情況下有意外<br />\n乘客係咪都係向車主/司機追討<br />\n保險公司都係唔會賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你理解都幾正確架啦<br />\n<br />\n不過有咩事其實都可以搵保險公司賠左先<br />\n保險公司可以再追討司機<br />\n<br />\n不過都要睇咩情況 唔係必然"},{"pid":"267eb996322df1a0320814d6bb8491d54608035c","tid":374173,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賠,下年個保費會加,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估保險咁易比你賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係架 保險不嬲唔係比客賺錢 係賺風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你可以諗下客無買咪賺保費 但出事自己揹咁解<br />\n<br />\n其實揹到的確可以自己做自己保險既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8767e3fa75be9981d10a71903348f3e6b240e07","tid":374173,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Delay/Cancel ➡問航空公司拎證明➡confirm自己份旅遊保有更改行程保障，並滿足條件➡改/買機票（留低登機證）➡如果當地有額外住宿keep埋單➡返香港Claim➡保險公司賠用左既錢<br />\n<br />\n想問問呢個情況有咩條件需要滿足？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n間間條件都唔同 一般黎講都係要天氣 罷工 天災之類既野<br />\n<br />\n同埋要一定鐘數"},{"pid":"21a4b6d50bae7ca6d0e9237274ca0e803073ad84","tid":374173,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>例如我香港直飛日本班機取消左<br />\n我另外買單程飛日本<br />\n咁ok 唔ok 呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要睇取消到咩地步 同埋你份保險包咩"},{"pid":"839fa3f8b5ff0bdc94a3629c7ccb3768c32778a3","tid":374173,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔敢答你 但我估銀行會輕鬆d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a266d93a0fcbbe4e2d5e17cfa5eb7c1f8f8331a","tid":374173,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保誠旅遊保險<br />\n搭車時漏左個袋（3000前後），同書， mp3 機係車<br />\n其實有冇得賠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常都會賠呀 但留意不保事項<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搵你agent問啦 呢個情況唔難claim"},{"pid":"1146d4f2930f11d5804391abfe9829bf4561df15","tid":374173,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>claim完咪加保費囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n車保係 其餘都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁今次用左咪白白冇左個NCB?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白白....都claim左車價啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次點計都係claim錢抵架啦"},{"pid":"61907c15e43f414396a5cc903b546aaa17056c6c","tid":374173,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在香港搵食的保險公司食水噉深，賠多一百次，保險公司都仍然大把錢！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議你開一間 或者訓身買保險股<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6abaee421d51ffe7545ddfd922e6e8f0cea1801","tid":374173,"uid":62079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>在香港搵食的保險公司食水噉深，賠多一百次，保險公司都仍然大把錢！</blockquote><br />\n大陸仔返天涯la.</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢一定係講緊Life, GI食水深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4508f356745cda49d9fd2ff64d1793fb78ff77ec","tid":374173,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:51:44.000Z","msg":"根本香港GI保費就鬥平鬥賤，大把保險公司蝕住做。同Life完全唔同生態"},{"pid":"99709ba2e4f0da5a8d128fe4b818db